        <title>5分钟极速生成座位表</title>
        <link>https://www.stepbystep.cf/archives/students-table/</link>
        <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jun 2022 09:59:31 +0800</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://www.stepbystep.cf/archives/students-table/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://img.gejiba.com/images/3b686bd0461bac0d40f6f4fe05c7643b.webp" alt="Featured image of post 5分钟极速生成座位表" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://ybygjylj.lanzouf.com/izQaB0719g2b&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;软件下载&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;一拍照&#34;&gt;一、拍照&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;让同学们按学号顺序排队，依次拍照，并让同学们坐好后依次填写座位表格（只填学号）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;二打包上传电脑&#34;&gt;二、打包上传电脑&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;用微信将打包的图片上传至电脑并解压&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;三批量重命名序号&#34;&gt;三、批量重命名序号&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;将图片移动到软件目录的img文件夹，运行bat程序&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;四填写表单生成表格&#34;&gt;四、填写表单生成表格&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;依次按照提示输入信息，位置按照座位表格顺序输入，用空格分隔开&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;五打印或保存电子版&#34;&gt;五、打印或保存电子版&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ctrl＋p即可弹出打印窗口&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1FN4y1g7HQ/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;bilibili传送门&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/stepbystepcode/students-table&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;github传送门&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
        </item>
        <item>
        <title>安卓手机投屏指南</title>
        <link>https://www.stepbystep.cf/archives/android-casting/</link>
        <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jun 2022 13:21:12 +0900</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://www.stepbystep.cf/archives/android-casting/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://img.gejiba.com/images/6b28b6f6a09bf792403efe3d8b012450.png" alt="Featured image of post 安卓手机投屏指南" /&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;一下载scrcpy并解压缩&#34;&gt;一、下载scrcpy并解压缩&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://hub.fastgit.xyz/Genymobile/scrcpy/releases/download/v1.24/scrcpy-win64-v1.24.zip&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;点击下载&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;将其解压至一个稳定安全不会误删除的地方，本例为：&lt;code&gt;D:\scrcpy&lt;/code&gt;，确保进入目录后可以看到scrcpy.exe&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;二配置环境变量&#34;&gt;二、配置环境变量&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;此电脑（资源管理器）右键属性→高级系统设置→环境变量→双击上半部分窗格里Path→新建→浏览→选择刚刚解压的（包含scrcpy.exe的）文件夹→确定→确定→确定&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;三打开手机开发者模式&#34;&gt;三、打开手机开发者模式&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;找到手机信息（包含手机型号、芯片的信息页），快速反复点击版本号，直到提示“您已经进入开发者模式”，然后返回，找到开发者模式→USB调试→开启→（确定开启）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;四投屏&#34;&gt;四、投屏&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;将手机与电脑用数据线连接后，打开电脑终端，输入scrcpy后回车，在手机上确认，即可在电脑屏幕上看到你的手机屏幕。&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
        </item>
        <item>
        <title>computer beginner&#39;s manual 📔</title>
        <link>https://www.stepbystep.cf/archives/computer-tutorial/</link>
        <pubDate>Sun, 06 Mar 2022 06:28:31 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://www.stepbystep.cf/archives/computer-tutorial/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://img.gejiba.com/images/dc28dd597dffccfbf3d871509da52d31.webp" alt="Featured image of post computer beginner&#39;s manual 📔" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you have already learned the basics of computer operation (switching on and off, clicking on the mouse and keyboard&amp;hellip;) The next step you should learn is the principles of computer use.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;general-rules&#34;&gt;General rules&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;i-courage&#34;&gt;I. Courage&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some people say I was born to know how to use a computer, but this is actually not true. The key to being able to use a computer is your attitude towards it. You need to treat the computer as a toy, not a tool, and you need to treat the system and software as a game. As long as you don&amp;rsquo;t go messing around with system settings and other dangerous areas, you generally won&amp;rsquo;t break your computer. So with that said: be brave! Be brave and try to gain experience. Don&amp;rsquo;t be afraid of this or that. You cower, you can never see the other side of the victory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;ii-check&#34;&gt;II. check&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There will not be a problem, on &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.bing.com/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Bing&lt;/a&gt; search a search. Don&amp;rsquo;t use Baidu anymore, it&amp;rsquo;s all ads and useless miscellaneous information. Remember, look up before you ask.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;iii-remember&#34;&gt;III. Remember&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When you learn a skill, remember it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;iv-practice&#34;&gt;IV. practice&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Practice hard, try more and summarize more&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;v-understand&#34;&gt;V. Understand&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Never expect the most detailed tutorials, you need to comprehend it yourself and explore the unknown world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;big-no-nos&#34;&gt;Big no-no&amp;rsquo;s&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;put the file on the desktop&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;install the software to the C drive&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;download software from the Internet without discrimination&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;naming the software installation directory and system user name in Chinese&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;install-software&#34;&gt;install software&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first problem that plagues many computer beginners is installing software.
Open &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;pc.qq.com&#34; &gt;pc.qq.com&lt;/a&gt;, search for the software name in the search bar on the upper right, and then find the software you want in the results, click the &amp;lt;span style=&amp;ldquo;color:red&amp;rdquo; on the green button on the right &amp;ldquo;&amp;gt;Small Arrow&lt;/span&gt; and then click &lt;span style=&#34;color:red&#34;&gt;Normal Download&lt;/span&gt;. Open the downloaded installation package, 95% of the software can customize the installation location during installation. Create a new folder on the D drive and name it the same as the software name (in English, capitalized). If the software name is in Chinese, please spell it in pinyin with capitalized first letter, without spaces (such as Baofengyingyin: Baofeng), do not add any Punctuation. Select the directory to install. Pay attention to detail options when installing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;uninstall-software&#34;&gt;Uninstall software&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;first-preparations&#34;&gt;First preparations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click the link below to download Geek Uninstaller
&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://disk.stepbystep.cf/d/geek.exe&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Click me to download&lt;/a&gt;
Save it in the D drive and create a new folder (named Geek)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;uninstall-method&#34;&gt;Uninstall method&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Open geek, find the software you want to uninstall, right-click to uninstall. Follow the prompts to uninstall in the pop-up uninstallation window. Then go back to the geek window and click delete. Then close geek after the progress bar is complete.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
        </item>
        <item>
        <title>极致美化windows终端</title>
        <link>https://www.stepbystep.cf/archives/beautify-windows-terminal/</link>
        <pubDate>Mon, 21 Feb 2022 12:14:24 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://www.stepbystep.cf/archives/beautify-windows-terminal/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://img.gejiba.com/images/565ad253511245591b93e2d79ec3c6f3.webp" alt="Featured image of post 极致美化windows终端" /&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;一下载文件并校验文件完整性&#34;&gt;一、下载文件并校验文件完整性&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://hub.fastgit.xyz/PowerShell/PowerShell/releases/latest&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;点击下载新版Powershell(PowerShell-x.x.x-win-x64.msi)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://hub.fastgit.xyz/git-for-windows/git/releases/latest&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;点击下载Git(Git-x.xx.x-64-bit.exe)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://hub.fastgit.xyz/JanDeDobbeleer/oh-my-posh/releases/latest&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;点击下载oh-my-posh(install-amd64.exe)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://ybygjylj.lanzouf.com/iYuZD06mepjc&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;点击下载Checksum&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;二安装git&#34;&gt;二、安装Git&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;三安装nerd-font字体&#34;&gt;三、安装Nerd Font字体&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;推荐JetBrainsMono&lt;/em&gt;
&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://hub.fastgit.xyz/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts/releases/download/v2.1.0/JetBrainsMono.zip&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;点击下载&lt;/a&gt;
下载解压后选中全部ttf文件，右键，安装&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;四安装windows-terminal-preview&#34;&gt;四、安装Windows Terminal Preview&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Windows 应用商店搜索Windows Terminal Preview，并安装。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;如果由于网络原因无法打开应用商店，可以&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://apps.microsoft.com/store/search/windows%20terminal%20preview&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;点击此处&lt;/a&gt;选择Windows Terminal Preview，复制详情页地址，粘贴到&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://store.rg-adguard.net/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;该网站&lt;/a&gt;，选择Retail渠道，下载安装包(最后一个)。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;五安装新版powershell&#34;&gt;五、安装新版PowerShell&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;一路下一步即可，建议安装到D盘的Powershell文件夹。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;打开Windows Terminal Preview的设置，选择左侧Windows PowerShell，路径改为安装的刚刚安装的D盘中Powershell文件夹中pwsh.exe，并在最后加上 -nologo参数。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-fallback&#34; data-lang=&#34;fallback&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;D:\PowerShell\7\pwsh.exe  -nologo
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;六安装oh-my-posh&#34;&gt;六、安装oh-my-posh&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在D盘新建目录oh-my-posh，将oh-my-posh安装至该目录。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;七设置字体与配色方案&#34;&gt;七、设置字体与配色方案&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;推荐Dracula
在设置中打开JSON文件，找到&amp;quot;schemes&amp;quot;，在中括号中添加（注意除了最后一个，每个大括号块后的逗号）&lt;/p&gt;
